it.bradipao.lib.descharts

类 StyledChartPointSerie

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.bradipao.lib.descharts.StyledChartPointSerie

  • public class StyledChartPointSerie
extends java.lang.Object
    StyledChartPointSerie() class represents a line graph to be plotted. It contains dataset of styled X,Y couples (StyledChartPoint class) and width property.

      • addPoint

        public void addPoint(StyledChartPoint point)
        Adds a point to the ArrayList of points dataset. If the mOrderonx property is not enabled, point is added at the end of the ArrayList, else it is added in the position that preserves crescent ordering of X coordinate.

      • shiftPoint

        public void shiftPoint(StyledChartPoint point,
                       int max)
        Shifts a point to the ArrayList of points dataset. Adding is done calling addPoint(), then points are removed from the beginning of the list untile there are maximum max points in the list.
